This repository is the open reference implementation of Iterative
Reasoning Graphs (IRG). It is licensed CC BY-SA 4.0.

A separate commercial product line built on these ideas — including the
Reason DSL runtime, governance/EIE monitoring pipeline, and other
enterprise components — is published under different terms and is
not part of this repository.

If you use this work, please attribute "Arcus Labs — IRG Reference"
and include a link to this repository.
